{
  "stem": "11964.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he either rented or bought-- I don't know how he did that-- a truck and loaded us on the truck.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And within a half an hour, we disappeared.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he took us to a river.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we come there, and it's night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he instructs us what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There are going to be boats, small boats there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there are going to be a couple of people to each boat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the Danube, that separated Russian from the American zone in Austria.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They are going to take you to the American zone, and then you are set free.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So under the cover of the night, we got to the other side of the Danube.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came off in a very infamous place called Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We come there, and at that time, of course, we have learned about all these camps.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It seems that the American MPs established transit camp outside of Mauthausen, which was called Wells, W-E-L-L-S.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And indeed, it was a camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was surrounded by barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was guarded by MPs with drawn weapons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we got there, and they put us up in barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sleeping accommodations were straw sacks stuffed with straw, which we didn't mind.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But what we did mind is that we weren't treated well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One time, I remember, at 2 o'clock in the morning the MPs stormed into our barracks, because they said that somebody stole a can of peaches.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they made us get up, and they were searching the sacks of straw for the can of peaches.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But gratefully, gratefully and thankfully, we were about to leave very soon to a displaced persons camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But one of the things that did happen at Wells, they registered us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They registered us and they accounted for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
